Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.68,0:01:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,PRINCESS OF THE SKY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.56,0:01:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.25,0:01:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you inside Sam's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sam Carraclough is next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, aren't you George?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.11,0:01:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You have grown a lot since\Nthe last time I met you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a very young child!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, didn't you enter in a wrong home?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.10,0:02:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a mistake again ...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not George, but John...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me remember. John, John...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As I recall that the son of Sam\NCarraclough was named George!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's definitely me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.67,0:02:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I'm John.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Mr. Dohan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello Melissa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's on the top floor,\NI'll take you to him immediately!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a wonderful dog,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it's one of the best species!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is the matter?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Go all this distance to see me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.98,0:02:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This... Are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that true? That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I saw him somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your father's boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what a man like him looks like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't judge people only by their looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, even if you look at them from near,\Nyou won't be able to judge directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What about time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.76,0:03:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In a way, the decision suddenly came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.94,0:03:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I received a call earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Will come from the sky tomorrow\Nat 11 o'clock, until the coal is achieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think the time is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I came to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,From the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an airplane!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about the plane...\NYou remember that plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The first meeting between us\Nwas because of that plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's amazing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, get away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't approach of it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This bike is not mine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh! You are...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you do in a place like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where is your house?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eh!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here you are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well okay, are you okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh! Ah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, if that plane had not been there,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,we would not have met!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You grow a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,within one year you became very big!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you a quiet sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be great if I could fly in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered, in that plane...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're so boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I do this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Would we really need a red carpet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We will not be rude as long\Nas we clean it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No no no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like a newspaper seller\Nor anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When the owner sees all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey these notes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,These! Put it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Something strange happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a man from the management coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the manager hasn't\Ncome out of the office yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What is special about that man\Nfrom the management?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The money the manager gets from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the owner of this entire mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:06:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter, get to work immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rare to see you here early on a weekend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like it, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for that, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, "Not for that"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Lassie came to help us\Ngraze the sheep, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie is Lassie, and I am me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that! Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to sponsor it at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but what are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to see the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the red carpet, but will it be good?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it better not to open the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:08:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if you ran all your pace to buy one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do I get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important to work faithfully in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he should see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No no, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eh! Sam! Sam!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That person! That...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want him here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my God, this is exhausting...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Banson!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're good at your job no matter\Nhow wine you drink, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, it's better\Nnot to drink in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Pff!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems very high.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that? Who is flying it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the same plane!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't it land?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The sheep are blocking their way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh I understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather the sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:10:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait!\N- Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Priscilla, I have work to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me to the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you take me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The staff don't work well,\Nso I'll just check it out myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to stay in your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandfather always talks\Nlike that when I go with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You gathered the sheep so we can land, right?\NThank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, we have to leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.06,0:11:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But we couldn't land without it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I should thank to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this pasture belong to this village?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The village?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, that place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should look at\Nthe surrounding areas closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your home there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You are good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, isn't the time to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You never help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see the plane landing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie, is that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We are not soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:13:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We must show loyalty to the original owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too much, to stop working for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought cleaning alone was enough, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Upon arrival, we were assembled\Nin an organized manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Pff! They are just idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is not it wonderful, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, but it's a bit boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I brought you the most beautiful horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have prepared for you this horse\Nwho has very beautiful hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact its hair is really beautiful but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it run?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.52,0:13:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It could do it easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To the village houses!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But the weather is totally cloudy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The horse can run a little, but not that hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what will happen\Nto me if something happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, is it okay with just a few?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When I finish I will leave immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But no problem if you take me on a quick tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I said no... I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay, you scoundrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let 's run away, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Heinz, right? Why did he lie to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't run well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,However we are still abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That brown dog was working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go to that village slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,These houses are connected altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what is inside this village?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All I wanted was to allow me only a short trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well don't matter, I'll have a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the mine building?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where the sheep house is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet I'm still lucky because of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.53,0:16:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it from Colin and was the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, hedgehog!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.24,0:16:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't bother you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.22,0:16:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your voice is too loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You who were on that plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.79,0:17:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wet! Moistened!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For the second time we can\Ncontinue to work at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad I got here\Nbefore the rain got stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Much mud...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The manager appeared to\Nhave been hit hard in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He went to the next room to crawl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This man will make things harder when\Nhe brings his granddaughter with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,His granddaughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.22,0:17:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This Duke is very proud of his granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how his granddaughter looks like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:17:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best dessert in Colin's shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Colin?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You were wandering around the village,\Ndidn't you? That store...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The only place to sell this dessert\Nin the village is Colin's shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not jam or canned food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a candy store?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sell medicines, seeds and also\Nworks as a post-office.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Many things, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It works to deliver or receive requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even today Colin can't play with me\Nbecause of the work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor little one...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Colin does not hate this work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If there are no customers,\Nhe just reads his favorite books.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understand, he likes reading, doesn't he?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He read many books.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,His favorite books are adventure-type,\Nwhich he begins with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What made you laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:18:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is because Colin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When someone enters he is very surprised\Nand hides the book immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what makes me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he hiding it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Colin reads books sold in the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So he thinks it's bad to read\Nin front of customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.27,0:19:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one cares about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have read some of\Nthe adventure books from Colin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fun, though
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't read that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that book?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"Five Weeks in a Balloon".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When I read it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt lucky because I could fly in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have you come by plane?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope to fly high in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.72,0:19:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:20:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To the Rocky Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rocky Castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's in the south of the village!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's after the flower field.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a large rocky hill\Nthat looks like a castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When we reach the top\Nwe can see the sky more broadly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If I thought about it, it would be
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,my responsibility if she\Nfell off the horse and hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.48,0:20:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miss! Miss!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad, he's already arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you stop joking,\Nyou will be punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.06,0:20:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Um?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing wrong, faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pretend to run away from you,\Nand lock it with your other hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It moves a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like a gem, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It is more beautiful than a jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miss!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Heinz! I made you\Ngo through a difficult time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You woke up late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered, I didn't askd her name...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I forgot to ask him his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That brown dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps that boy is a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.03,0:21:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to go back\Nbefore we're punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.26,0:22:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No good! No good!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie, that girl has come{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to my home!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.35,0:22:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? What does Sandy plans with my mom?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.85,0:22:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this is strange!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How did you know my house?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.91,0:22:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode:\NTHE FIRST CAKE WE MAKE{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be sure to watch!{\i0}
